## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="135be-159">下面的代码示例将 `pgBrush` 的几何变换重置为恒等。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="135be-159">The following code example resets the geometric transform of `pgBrush` to identity.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="135be-160">假定 `myPath` 是现有 <xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.GraphicsPath>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="135be-160">It is assumed that `myPath` is an existing <xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.GraphicsPath>.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
PathGradientBrush pgBrush = new PathGradientBrush(myPath);  
 pgBrush.ResetTransform();  
```
